highlights.text: “Um Dia Te Levo Comigo / Do Brasil à Argentina - Ao Vivo” by Panda and MJ Records is the highest new entry on Top Songs Brazil at #166.
“Lapada Dela - Ao Vivo” by Grupo Menos É Mais and Matheus Fernandes has been on Top Songs Brazil the longest, at 892 days straight.
Henrique & Juliano has the most spots on Top Songs Brazil. “Última Saudade - Ao Vivo” is the highest at #10.
“Respeitando Minha Saudade - Ao Vivo” by Diego & Victor Hugo is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Brazil, up 96 spots at #80.
